about.summary: Turn Python scripts into handouts with Markdown and figures

name: handout
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "handout" %}
{% set version = "1.1.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "dbe5da9b422fa937b94a1a5221ce99387ebd75fe97ab4255e49b26d846b8614b" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - handout

about:
  home: "http://github.com/danijar/handout"
  license: "Apache-2.0"
  license_family: "APACHE"
  license_file: "LICENSE-2.0.txt"
  summary: "Turn Python scripts into handouts with Markdown and figures"
  doc_url: "http://github.com/danijar/handout"
  dev_url: "http://github.com/danijar/handout"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - notestaff
